    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1864-06-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1864-06-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="394" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d394">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Lord Lyons</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Seward</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>,</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1864-06-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 5, 1864.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> On the 21th of April you were good enough
                            to inform me that the military commission, which investigated the case
                            of Mr. James McHugh had reported that, in their judgment, he should be
                            released. It appears, however, from a letter which I have received from
                            him, that he was still at Fort Lafayette on the 31st ultimo, more than a
                            month afterwards.</p>
                <pb facs="0649" n="629" xml:id="pg_629"/>
                <p>I earnestly beg you to call the immediate attention of the proper
                            authorities to the case, and to move them to release Mr. McHugh without
                            further delay.</p>
                <p>I have the honor to be, sir, with the highest consideration, your most
                            obedient, humble servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>LYONS.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>, <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
